OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1773249075
OL,3,CEddie Howe urges players to seize
OL,4,Cchance to write names in Newcastle
OL,5,Cfolklore
OL,7,FEddie Howe has challenged his players
OL,8,Fto write themselves into Newcastle's
OL,9,Fhistory alongside Tino Asprilla and
OL,10,Fhis team-mates as they prepare for
OL,11,Ftheir Champions League showdown with
OL,12,FBarcelona.
OL,14,FIn September 1997, Colombian
OL,15,Finternational Asprilla scored a hat-
OL,16,Ftrick as the Magpies defeated the
OL,17,FSpanish side 3-2 in the same
OL,18,Fcompetition in a game which is spoken
OL,19,Fof in reverent tones on Tyneside to
OL,20,Fthis day.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/9
