OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1773249075
OL,3,CEddie Howe urges players to seize
OL,4,Cchance to write names in Newcastle
OL,5,Cfolklore
OL,7,FHowe was a 19-year-old trying to make
OL,8,Fhis way at Bournemouth at the time but
OL,9,Fremembers the game well and knows the
OL,10,Fplace in holds in the hearts of both
OL,11,Fthose who witnessed it and subsequent
OL,12,Fgenerations.
OL,14,F"You couldn't not watch that game," he
OL,15,Fsaid ahead of Tuesday's game. "It was
OL,16,Fon terrestrial television. It was one
OL,17,Fof those legendary games.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
