OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1773249075
OL,3,CEddie Howe urges players to seize
OL,4,Cchance to write names in Newcastle
OL,5,Cfolklore
OL,7,F"You want people in future years to be
OL,8,Ftalking about this team. Tino Asprilla
OL,9,Fgets the hat-trick, a couple of them
OL,10,Ffrom Keith Gillespie's delivery on the
OL,11,Fright. I want our players to be talked
OL,12,Fabout in the same way, 20, 30, 40
OL,13,Fyears later."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
