CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1773249075
OL,3,CEddie Howe urges players to seize
OL,4,Cchance to write names in Newcastle
OL,5,Cfolklore
OL,7,FIn the wake of Saturday night's FA Cup
OL,8,Ffifth-round exit at the hands of
OL,9,FManchester City, Howe described
OL,10,FBarcelona's second visit to Tyneside
OL,11,Fthis season ` they won 2-1 in the
OL,12,Fopening game of the group phase in
OL,13,FSeptember thanks to Marcus Rashford's
OL,14,Fdouble ` as "the biggest game in the
OL,15,Fclub's history".
OL,17,FAsked if that was a reflection of the
OL,18,Fromanticism surrounding the fixture,
OL,19,Fthe 48-year-old said: "To a point,
OL,20,Fyes. But there are also only 16 teams
OL,21,Fleft and we're one of them.
OL,26,@vD@MOUwD@OO]{D@WOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1773249075
OL,3,CEddie Howe urges players to seize
OL,4,Cchance to write names in Newcastle
OL,5,Cfolklore
OL,7,F"It's an opportunity to grab a moment
OL,8,Fthat we may never get again. You never
OL,9,Fknow what life brings tomorrow, let
OL,10,Falone future seasons. We don't want to
OL,11,Fwaste that opportunity. We don't want
OL,12,Fto kick ourselves or think, 'What
OL,13,Fif?'. This is a moment for us to grab."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
