FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1773249075
OL,3,CEddie Howe urges players to seize
OL,4,Cchance to write names in Newcastle
OL,5,Cfolklore
OL,7,FNewcastle, who head for the Nou Camp
OL,8,Fnext Wednesday, reached the last 16 in
OL,9,FEuropean club football's premier
OL,10,Fcompetition during the 2002-03
OL,11,Fcampaign, when there were two group
OL,12,Fstages, but have never before played
OL,13,Fin the knockout rounds and would
OL,14,Fcreate a new first if they made it to
OL,15,Fthe quarter-finals.
OL,17,FHowe said: "We're going to need to
OL,18,Fbreak new ground in terms of
OL,19,Fperformance level, so if there's a
OL,20,Ftime for us to be at our absolute
OL,21,Fbest, it's in these two games."
OL,26,@yD@LOU}D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
