CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1773249075
OL,3,CEddie Howe urges players to seize
OL,4,Cchance to write names in Newcastle
OL,5,Cfolklore
OL,7,FIf they are to do that, they may need
OL,8,Fleft-back Lewis Hall to be at his
OL,9,Fabsolute best to keep a tight rein on
OL,10,FLamine Yamal, although he is far from
OL,11,Ffazed by the prospect. The teenage
OL,12,Fwinger was injured for the game
OL,13,Fbetween the sides earlier in the
OL,14,Fseason but is fully fit for the round
OL,15,Fof 16.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
