PN,42608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1773249075
OL,3,CEddie Howe urges players to seize
OL,4,Cchance to write names in Newcastle
OL,5,Cfolklore
OL,7,F"I think it goes without saying he's
OL,8,Fobviously a special talent," Hall
OL,9,Fsaid. "I've seen him play in enough
OL,10,FChampions League games. I know what
OL,11,Fhe's about. So for me, if I was to be
OL,12,Fselected, I'd be really looking
OL,13,Fforward to it.
OL,15,F"I want to test myself against the
OL,16,Fbest players in the world and there's
OL,17,Fno better opportunity to do so than
OL,18,Fthe game tomorrow."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOUzD@SO]
